## Skills

Invokable skills (read `.cursor/skills/<name>/SKILL.md` and follow the workflow):

| Skill                | Trigger                                                                                                              | Purpose                                                                                                                                                                               |
| -------------------- | -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| `/work`              | "work", "go", "execute", "grind"                                                                                     | Autonomous task execution loop                                                                                                                                                        |
| `/plan`              | "plan", "make a plan", "/plan"                                                                                       | Create a rich project plan with codebase analysis                                                                                                                                     |
| `/investigate`       | "/investigate", "investigate what to do next"                                                                        | High-level investigation; dispatches reviewer in research mode                                                                                                                        |
| `/evolve`            | "/evolve", "evolve the last plan", after plan completion                                                             | Post-plan pattern mining; analyses task diffs to surface implementation anti-patterns and route learnings to agent templates and docs                                                 |
| `/audit-performance` | "/audit-performance", "audit perf", "performance review", "find bottlenecks"                                         | Performance audit; dispatches parallel ferret-search scanners (schema, queries, hotpaths, anti-patterns, Dolt) with a pre-compute race agent that stores shared context in task notes |
| `/clean-up-shop`     | "clean up shop", "clean house", "no jobs in flight", "clean up worktrees", "remove worktrees", after a /work session | Post-session housekeeping: return main checkout to `main`, merge completed worktrees, remove worktree directories, delete merged branches, process pending learnings                  |
